### Register user
POST http://localhost:8081/api/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@demo.com",
  "password": "$2a$10$...",
  "fullName": "Test User",
  "role": "USER"
}

### Login user
POST http://localhost:8081/api/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@gmail.com",
  "password": "12345678"
}
